|  France Launches Anti-Spam Platform                                |
|   from the more-blacklists dept.                                   |
|   posted by ScuttleMonkey on Sunday May 13, @10:19 (Spam)          |
|   http://it.slashdot.org/article.pl?sid=07/05/13/130250            |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

[0]njondet writes "French-law.net reports that the French government has
[1]just launched 'Signal Spam', an [2]anti-spam platform created in
association with public entities and private companies, such as
Microsoft. Internet users will be able to report spam messages by mailing
them to this platform which will act as a centralised monitor of spamming
activities. The platform will generate a blacklist and help initiate
prosecutions against spammers."

Discuss this story at:
    http://it.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=07/05/13/130250

Links:
